<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-344-699  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 344 699.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>DEC Professional  Feb 1989 v8 n2 p162(4).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>BRS Information Technologies' BRS-Search. (Software Review) (Fromthe Lab) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Miller, David B.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>BRS Information Technologies' $7,500 BRS-Search 4.1 softwarepackage provides a system to archive Mass-11 documents into adatabase.andP;  Several options provide flexibility when searching fordocuments, such as the SearchMate query screen that displays anumber of search examples, and a time-saving method that allowsthe easy use of previous searches.andP;  A Special Function menuprovides a way to customize search parameters, and users canspecify the desired default logical operator.andP;  Display optionsinclude a Full display, a Brief display and a Context display.andO;Other options include the Limit commands, which let users narrowsearches by forcing BRS to look for specific criteria in one ofits data base fields, and the Delete, Thesaurus and CROSS DatabaseSearching options.andP;  BRS-Search's installation is discussed.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   BRS Information Technologies (products).andO;Product:   BRS-Search 4.1 (Computer program).andO;Topic:     EvaluationSoftware PackagesDocument Management SystemsInformation Storage and Retrieval.andO;Feature:   illustrationtable.andO;Caption:   BRS-Search, Mass-11 Version. (table)andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>